{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban on sale of disposable BBQs",
        "additional_details": "With increasing pressure on waste management systems and growing climate-related fire risk, we believe action is needed to reduce avoidable harm caused by these products. We are therefore asking the Government to:\r\n \r\n1. Introduce a UK-wide ban on the sale of disposable BBQs\r\n2. Encourage safer, reusable alternatives through public guidance\r\n3. Work with retailers to support the transition away from single-use outdoor cooking products",
        "background": "We want the Government to introduce a nationwide ban on the sale of single-use disposable barbecues. Disposable BBQs are increasingly linked to preventable wildfires, which  poses a serious risk to public safety, wildlife, and emergency services. Also, disposable BBQs contribute to unnecessary waste",
